sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Wk as Worker
    participant H as Handler
    participant R as Redis
    Wk->>H: POST .../callback {wake_id w_a, generation 7, done:true}
    H->>R: EVALSHA ack.lua — fence check
    Note over R: token gen 7 == cur · wake w_a == cur · pass
    R-->>H: OK · cursor advanced · wake_id cleared
    H-->>Wk: 200 {ok:true, next_wake:false}
    Wk->>H: POST .../callback {wake_id w_a, generation 7} — replay
    H->>R: EVALSHA ack.lua — fence check
    Note over R: cur wake_id now empty · w_a is stale
    R-->>H: FENCED
    H-->>Wk: 409 {error code FENCED}
